If you intend to re-create this app (and you should!), do the following:\
1. In Xcode, File > New > New Project \
2. On the left-side navigator, select iOS > Application, and in the right-side detail area, select "Single View Application" \
3. Fill in the following details:\
	Enter a project name in the "Product Name" textbox; \
	enter something in the "Company Identifier" textbox, ONLY IF IT'S EMPTY!; \
	choose iPhone on the "Device Family" drop-down list; and\
	leave all checkboxes at their defaults (Storyboard and Automatic Reference Counting checked, and Unit Tests un-checked) \
4. Choose a folder / storage location, and un-check (clear) the "Source Control" checkbox\
